---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Loire Digital - Sites web professionnels à Saint-Étienne | Sans blabla"
  description="Studio digital spécialisé pour artisans et commerçants de la Loire. Sites web modernes, design premium, prix transparents. Réponse sous 24h garantie."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative py-24 md:py-32 bg-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="mb-8 animate-fadeIn">
          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-gray-pale text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700"
          >
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-600 rounded-full"></span>
            Studio Digital · Saint-Étienne
          </span>
        </div>

        <h1
          class="text-6xl md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl font-black text-black mb-8 leading-[0.95] animate-fadeIn"
          style="letter-spacing: -0.04em; animation-delay: 0.1s;"
        >
          Un site web qui fait vendre,<br />
          <span class="text-blue-600">pas juste beau.</span>
        </h1>

        <p
          class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-gray-700 font-medium mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto animate-fadeIn"
          style="animation-delay: 0.2s;"
        >
          Sites rapides, design pro, prix honnêtes. Pour artisans et commerçants de Saint-Étienne qui veulent des résultats.
        </p>

        <div
          class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mb-12 animate-fadeIn"
          style="animation-delay: 0.4s;"
        >
          <a href="/devis" class="btn-blue text-lg shadow-lg shadow-blue-600/30">
            Devis gratuit – Réponse sous 24h
          </a>
          <a href="/portfolio" class="btn-secondary text-lg"> Voir nos réalisations </a>
        </div>

        <div
          class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-8 text-sm text-gray-600 animate-fadeIn"
          style="animation-delay: 0.5s;"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Devis sous 24h</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Zéro surprise sur le prix</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Livré en 2-3 semaines</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    .animate-fadeIn {
      animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out forwards;
      opacity: 0;
    }
  </style>

  <!-- Sticky Chapter Navigation -->
  <nav
    id="chapter-nav"
    class="hidden lg:block fixed right-8 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-50 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 p-4"
  >
    <ul class="space-y-2">
      <li>
        <a
          href="#pourquoi"
          class="chapter-link block px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-50 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200"
        >
          Pourquoi
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a
          href="#services"
          class="chapter-link block px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-50 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200"
        >
          Services
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a
          href="#tarifs"
          class="chapter-link block px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-50 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200"
        >
          Tarifs
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a
          href="#realisations"
          class="chapter-link block px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-50 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200"
        >
          Réalisations
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a
          href="#process"
          class="chapter-link block px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-50 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200"
        >
          Process
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a
          href="#faq"
          class="chapter-link block px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-50 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200"
        >
          FAQ
        </a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <!-- Bento Grid - Pourquoi nous choisir -->
  <section id="pourquoi" class="py-16 md:py-24 section-pale">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="mb-16 text-center">
          <h2
            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-black mb-4"
            style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
          >
            Pourquoi Loire Digital ?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-text max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Simple, efficace, transparent.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Bento Grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-6 gap-4 auto-rows-fr">
          <!-- Grande boîte - Délai -->
          <div
            class="card-minimal bg-gray-50 md:col-span-2 md:row-span-2 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center p-8 md:p-12"
          >
            <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg
                class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-600"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Réactivité garantie</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-text leading-relaxed">
              Devis détaillé sous 24h. Pas de "je vous rappelle", on répond direct avec un vrai plan
              d'action.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Sécurité -->
          <div
            class="card-minimal bg-gray-50 md:col-span-2 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center p-8"
          >
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg
                class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-black mb-2">HTTPS automatique</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-text">
              Cadenas vert dès le jour 1. Vos clients ont confiance, Google vous classe mieux.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Tarifs transparents -->
          <div
            class="card-minimal bg-gray-50 md:col-span-2 p-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center"
          >
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg
                class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-black mb-2">Prix cash</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-text">
              Le prix du devis = le prix final. Pas de frais cachés, pas de "ah mais ça c'est en
              plus".
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Design sur-mesure -->
          <div
            class="card-minimal md:col-span-2 bg-blue-600 text-white p-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center"
          >
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-xl bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">100% sur-mesure</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-blue-100">
              Votre site ressemble à VOTRE business, pas au template WordPress de votre concurrent.
              Design unique garanti.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Performances -->
          <div
            class="card-minimal md:col-span-2 bg-green-600 text-white flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center p-8"
          >
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-xl bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg
                class="w-8 h-8 text-white"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Vitesse éclair</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-green-100">
              Chargement instantané sur mobile. Chaque seconde perdue = clients perdus. On optimise
              à fond.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Process clair - Grande carte -->
          <div class="card-minimal bg-gray-50 md:col-span-2 p-8">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg
                class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-black mb-3">Tout par écrit</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-text leading-relaxed">
              Zéro call. Tout par email. Vous avez une trace de chaque échange, chaque validation.
              Rien ne se perd, tout est clair.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bento Grid - Services -->
  <section id="services" class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="mb-16 text-center">
          <h2
            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-black mb-4"
            style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
          >
            Ce qu'on fait pour vous
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-text max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Du site vitrine classique à la refonte complète. Tout ce qu'il faut pour vendre en
            ligne.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Bento Grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 auto-rows-fr">
          <!-- Création - Large -->
          <div class="card-minimal md:col-span-2 md:row-span-2 p-8 flex flex-col">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg
                class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-black mb-4">Création de sites</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-text leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-grow">
              Sites web modernes optimisés pour la conversion. Design sur-mesure, code propre,
              performances maximales. De la page unique au site complet.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-2 mb-6">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-text">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-blue-600 rounded-full"></div>
                <span>Responsive design</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-text">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-blue-600 rounded-full"></div>
                <span>SEO optimisé</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-text">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-blue-600 rounded-full"></div>
                <span>Hébergement inclus</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a
              href="/services#creation"
              class="inline-flex items-center text-sm font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 mt-auto"
            >
              En savoir plus
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Refonte -->
          <div class="card-minimal md:col-span-2 p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg
                class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Refonte</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-text leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Modernisez votre site existant. Nouveau design, meilleures performances.
            </p>
            <a
              href="/services#refonte"
              class="inline-flex items-center text-sm font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700"
            >
              Découvrir
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- SEO Local -->
          <div class="card-minimal md:col-span-1 p-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-lg bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg
                class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-black mb-2">SEO</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-text">Référencement local</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Maintenance -->
          <div class="card-minimal md:col-span-1 p-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-lg bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg
                class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"
                ></path>
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-black mb-2">Maintenance</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-text">Support continu</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tarifs -->
  <section id="tarifs" class="py-16 md:py-24 section-pale">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="mb-16 text-center">
          <h2
            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-black mb-4"
            style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
          >
            Tarifs : du concret
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-text max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-4">
            Prix bas parce qu'on travaille vite, pas parce qu'on bâcle. Process rodé = moins de
            temps perdu = prix juste pour vous.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <!-- Starter -->
          <div class="card-minimal flex flex-col">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-2">Starter</h3>
            <div class="mb-6">
              <div class="text-5xl font-black text-black mb-1">400€</div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Paiement unique</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-6">
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1">Pour qui :</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Démarrer vite avec une présence propre en ligne</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-6">
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2">Inclus :</p>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm">
                  <svg
                    class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  >
                    <path
                      stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round"
                      stroke-width="2"
                      d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Landing page (1 page)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm">
                  <svg
                    class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  >
                    <path
                      stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round"
                      stroke-width="2"
                      d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Design sobre et professionnel</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm">
                  <svg
                    class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  >
                    <path
                      stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round"
                      stroke-width="2"
                      d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Formulaire de contact</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm">
                  <svg
                    class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  >
                    <path
                      stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round"
                      stroke-width="2"
                      d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Optimisation mobile</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
